claim.claim-text:
1. A cascaded interconnect system comprising:
one or more memory modules;
a memory controller for generating data frames that include one or more plurality of commands, each data frame comprised of the same number of transfers;
a memory bus, wherein the memory controller and the memory modules are interconnected by a packetized multi-transfer interface via the memory bus and wherein the frames are transmitted to the memory modules via the memory bus; and
a command decode matrix specifying command decodes and one or more associated transfers for locating the commands in the data frames.
